AZABU-JUBAN, TOKYO

178
00:10:11,444 --> 00:10:13,822
-Welcome back, guys.
-Hey!

179
00:10:13,905 --> 00:10:15,240
Looks amazing!

180
00:10:16,407 --> 00:10:18,493
How was it? Fun?

181
00:10:18,576 --> 00:10:22,080
-It was fun!
-We're all in pain.

182
00:10:22,163 --> 00:10:24,791
-It was great weather today.
-It was.

183
00:10:24,874 --> 00:10:26,126
It was warm.

184
00:10:27,877 --> 00:10:29,921
All of us getting together...

185
00:10:31,756 --> 00:10:33,091
Yeah, not since the incident.

186
00:10:33,174 --> 00:10:35,135
-Incident? It was a house meeting.
-Oh, yeah.

187
00:10:35,218 --> 00:10:38,513
What was the most memorable moment
for the two of you?

188
00:10:38,596 --> 00:10:41,057
-Of course, the "coward" incident.
-"Coward!"

189
00:10:41,141 --> 00:10:42,267
Oh, it's not the meat?

190
00:10:42,976 --> 00:10:44,978
No.
Though that was memorable, too.

191
00:10:45,061 --> 00:10:46,896
For me, it was the meat incident.

192
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:49,399
-Really?
-Maybe because it was recent.

193
00:10:49,482 --> 00:10:51,985
I was more surprised by the meat incident.

194
00:10:52,068 --> 00:10:53,736
Wish I'd seen it.

195
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:55,405
-It was your fault.
-Yeah!

196
00:10:55,488 --> 00:10:56,656
Why is it my fault?

197
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:59,450
I wasn't too involved though.

198
00:11:00,076 --> 00:11:01,119
-You did eat it.
-You did eat some.

199
00:11:01,202 --> 00:11:03,913
That couldn't be helped
because I was hungry.

200
00:11:03,997 --> 00:11:06,749
You owe me ramen, Hikaru.

201
00:11:09,252 --> 00:11:12,005
-What's with your expression?
-I'm suddenly feeling sad.

202
00:11:13,715 --> 00:11:15,925
It is sad, for real.

203
00:11:16,009 --> 00:11:18,386
I mean, you guys met here.

204
00:11:18,469 --> 00:11:20,054
-That's true.
-Right?

205
00:11:21,014 --> 00:11:23,683
Yeah, we were strangers before this.

206
00:11:25,268 --> 00:11:26,519
It's amazing.

207
00:11:48,291 --> 00:11:51,294
TATSUYA UCHIHARA, 24 YEARS OLD,
HAIR STYLIST

208
00:11:51,377 --> 00:11:54,005
MINORI NAKADA, 22 YEARS OLD, MODEL

209
00:11:54,088 --> 00:11:56,925
ARMAN BITARAF, 25 YEARS OLD,
ASPIRING FIREFIGHTER

210
