ARISA OHATA, 25 YEARS OLD,
HAT DESIGNER

211
00:12:00,178 --> 00:12:03,348
HIKARU OTA, 18 YEARS OLD,
MODEL, CONSTRUCTION WORKER

212
00:12:03,431 --> 00:12:06,893
NATSUMI SAITO, 26 YEARS OLD,
MODEL, ASPIRING ACTRESS

213
00:12:15,318 --> 00:12:17,195
I'm hungry.

214
00:12:17,278 --> 00:12:19,030
-You haven't eaten?
-I have.

215
00:12:19,113 --> 00:12:21,407
