Ramen! Ramen!

217
00:12:23,826 --> 00:12:24,869
Let's really go.

218
00:12:24,953 --> 00:12:27,914
Sure, I'll take you to a great place.

219
00:12:27,997 --> 00:12:29,958
-Let's go.
