221
00:12:32,669 --> 00:12:35,421
Wow,
from just four percent alcohol content?

222
00:12:38,549 --> 00:12:40,927
Ew, he's grossing me out.

223
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:42,971
You always say stuff like that.

224
00:12:43,054 --> 00:12:44,305
