-Breaks your heart?

228
00:12:51,938 --> 00:12:53,106
I like you very much.

229
00:12:53,189 --> 00:12:56,150
-More, more.
-Look into her eyes.

230
00:12:56,693 --> 00:12:57,944
I love you.

231
00:13:01,114 --> 00:13:02,156
Man, that was bad.

232
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:05,326
