236
00:13:14,002 --> 00:13:16,004
-Like a catfish?
-Ms. Catfish!

237
00:13:16,087 --> 00:13:17,714
He totally calls me Ms. Catfish.

238
00:13:17,797 --> 00:13:19,632
But you do kinda look like a catfish.

239
00:13:19,716 --> 00:13:21,676
Like a catfish...

240
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:23,594
You do have a catfish face.

241
00:13:23,678 --> 00:13:26,014
-I'm back.
-Welcome back.

242
00:13:26,097 --> 00:13:27,974
Oh, Arisa.

243
00:13:29,517 --> 00:13:31,352
Uchi's wasted.

244
00:13:31,436 --> 00:13:32,687
His face is all red.

245
00:13:32,770 --> 00:13:34,188
What about ramen?

