265
00:14:31,704 --> 00:14:32,914
with you.

266
00:14:33,998 --> 00:14:35,792
It's a little late now, but...

267
00:14:44,926 --> 00:14:47,929
Why don't you stay another week?

268
00:14:49,347 --> 00:14:50,890
Don't cry.

269
00:15:09,992 --> 00:15:11,536
