270
00:15:13,704 --> 00:15:16,582
Thank you for everything.

271
00:15:16,666 --> 00:15:18,584
Thank you.

272
00:15:18,668 --> 00:15:20,294
Thank you.

273
00:15:20,378 --> 00:15:21,879
Thank you.

274
00:15:21,963 --> 00:15:24,048
It was a fun six months.

275
00:15:24,132 --> 00:15:25,508
Six months.

276
00:15:26,384 --> 00:15:27,802
We had our arguments...

277
00:15:29,053 --> 00:15:30,430
but it was fun.

278
00:15:31,681 --> 00:15:33,850
Looking back, it was fun.

279
00:15:36,185 --> 00:15:37,478
Shall we?

280
00:15:51,325 --> 00:15:52,743
See you around, Hikaru.

281
00:15:55,746 --> 00:15:57,957
Bye.

282
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,625
See you, Arman.

283
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:02,462
Good luck.

284
00:16:02,545 --> 00:16:04,255
I'll see you.

285
00:16:06,299 --> 00:16:08,009
Thank you, Minori.

286
00:16:09,093 --> 00:16:10,261
Bye.

287
00:16:12,930 --> 00:16:14,849
-See ya!
-See ya.

288
00:16:14,932 --> 00:16:16,184
-Bye!
-Bye!

289
00:16:19,937 --> 00:16:20,980
Thank you.

290
00:16:21,063 --> 00:16:22,690
Thanks, Uchi and Minori.

291
00:16:22,773 --> 00:16:23,774
-Good luck!
-Bye!

292
00:16:26,068 --> 00:16:29,071
NISHI-AZABU, TOKYO

293
00:16:31,073 --> 00:16:32,992
So...

294
00:16:33,075 --> 00:16:36,287
I'm going to move into <i>Terrace House.</i>

295
00:16:36,871 --> 00:16:38,080
What?

296
00:16:38,164 --> 00:16:39,999
-Really?
-Yeah, really.

297
00:16:41,167 --> 00:16:43,211
-Yeah.
-When?

298
00:16:43,294 --> 00:16:45,713
-Tomorrow.
-What! Tomorrow?

299
00:16:45,796 --> 00:16:46,881
Are you serious?

300
00:16:48,299 --> 00:16:52,220
I want to experience co-op living.

301
00:16:52,303 --> 00:16:53,554
Seriously?

302
00:16:53,638 --> 00:16:57,517
